The Mages are a small but well-trained unit within the Kingdom of Kohlingen. The symbol of Mystra emblazoned on their cloaks, they work diligently as a branch of the Silver Dragons, under the command of the Magister.
This is a settlement guard insignia for the guard templates.

Welcome to the Kingdom of Kohlingen Portal Chamber!

These portals are provided for our family, friends, and allies, for their convenience. Please mind that the portals require regular maintenance and as such all save the Greengarden Portal are accompanied by a gold cost before you can use them.

The portals are as follows:

Green: Greengarden (Free)
Pink: The Dale (10gp)
Yellow: Djedet (50gp)
White: Barak Runedar Mountains (1000 gp)
